Interface PhotoSource.AuthorizationCompleteCallback

  • Enclosing interface:
    PhotoSource

    public static interface PhotoSource.AuthorizationCompleteCallback
    Callback interface for PhotoSource authorization completion.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void call(boolean canceled, boolean success, java.lang.String errorMessage)
      Called when PhotoSource authorization has completed.

    • Method Detail

      • call

        void call(boolean canceled,
        boolean success,
        java.lang.String errorMessage)
        Called when PhotoSource authorization has completed.
        Parameters:
        canceled - Flag telling if authorization was canceled by the user.
        success - Holds value indicating if authorization was successful. Value is set to true when user has successfully authorized to this PhotoSource, or false otherwise.
        errorMessage - Holds message to be shown to the user when authorization fails. Message is shown only if value is not null.
